#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.logit.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.logit"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit:1 of
msgid "Logit ufunc for ndarrays."
msgstr "ndarrays 的 Logit ufunc。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit:3 of
msgid ""
"The logit function is defined as logit(p) = log(p/(1-p)). Note that "
"logit(0) = -inf, logit(1) = inf, and logit(p) for p<0 or p>1 yields nan."
msgstr ""
"logit 函数定义为 logit(p) = log(p/(1-p))。注意 logit(0) = -inf，logit(1) "
"= inf，当 p<0 或 p>1 时 logit(p) 会返回 nan。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit:7 of
msgid "The ndarray to apply logit to element-wise."
msgstr "要对其逐元素应用 logit 的 ndarray。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit:9 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function results"
msgstr "用于函数结果的可选输出数组"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit:12 of
msgid ""
"An ndarray of the same shape as x. Its entries are logit of the "
"corresponding entry of x."
msgstr "一个与 x 形状相同的 ndarray。其每个条目是 x 对应条目的 logit 值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit:18 of
msgid ":func:`expit`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit:23 of
msgid ""
"As a ufunc logit takes a number of optional keyword arguments. For more "
"information see `ufuncs "
"<https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/reference/ufuncs.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"作为一个 ufunc，logit 接受若干个可选关键字参数。更多信息请参见 `ufuncs <"
"https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/reference/ufuncs.html>`_"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.logit:27 of
msgid ""
"`logit` has experimental support for Python Array API Standard compatible"
" backends in addition to NumPy. Please consider testing these features by"
" setting an environment variable ``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1`` and providing "
"CuPy, PyTorch, JAX, or Dask arrays as array arguments. The following "
"combinations of backend and device (or other capability) are supported."
msgstr ""
"`logit` 除了支持 NumPy 外，还实验性地支持兼容 Python Array API 标准的后端"
"。请考虑通过设置环境变量 ``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1`` 并提供 CuPy、PyTorch、JAX "
"或 Dask 数组作为数组参数来测试这些功能。以下为支持的后端与设备（或其他"
"能力）组合。"

